<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id77c051a6-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s460j"><num value="460j">§ 460j.</num><heading> Disposition of proceeds</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The proceeds from any sale made under this subchapter shall be covered into the Treasury of the United States as miscellaneous receipts.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id77c051a7-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/act/1956-08-06/ch987/s6">Aug. 6, 1956, ch. 987, § 6</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/70/1066">70 Stat. 1066</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
